{
  "stem": "5639.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was legal, through the bank.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was pittance.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember, once we received 50 mark.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we were called to the bank.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were allowed to leave the restricted area where we lived.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My father entered the post office, wearing an armband, as a Jew, with a piece of paper that he comes to collect 50 marks.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That is German.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The ultimate in German bureaucracy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It started very early.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were marked very early.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I cannot give you exactly the date, whether it was end of '39 or, I think-- or beginning of 1940.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At first, it was a white armband with a blue star of David.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were not Poles.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were never Poles.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were Jews who lived in Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What, integration?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The integration was ethnic and geographic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It doesn't matter where the Jew lived-- he remained a Jew.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The reason-- the only other effect that this integration could have had of us, that in-- up till-- up till 1943, we were treated, perhaps, as the few remaining German Jews.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't bother us very much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Our ghetto was small.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a very productive ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because we had a-- we had a German manager-- a German German-- who came to Bedzin and established-- who came to Bedzin as an employee of SS, and told them, I am surrounded by artisans Jews-- tailors, shoemakers, furriers, cobblers-- and why not to utilize them?",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he-- and they have got tools.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they can bring their tools, and their upkeep is not great, and their skills are enormous.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And let them work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I have got-- I didn't prepare that photograph.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he-- he was a disabled person.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was a polio victim.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was also a hemophiliac.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
